ional methodology underlying the\ncalculations described here is explained in our companion paper,\n$\\textit{Dynamical simulations of carotenoid photoexcited states using density\nmatrix renormalization group techniques}$, D. Manawadu, D. J. Valentine, and W.\nBarford, $\\textit{J. Chem. Theo. Comp.}$ (2023).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2022 05:34:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-07"}
