stacked tetralayer graphene as a\npromising platform for observing strongly correlated physics and topological\nsuperconductivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2022 14:47:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-06"}
